QuestData.Title: Surgical Strike
QuestData.Description:
Zandalari spiritbinders perform sacrifices to their gods, the beastcallers bend innocent skyscreamers to their will, and the jaguar warriors venture closer to us by the day.
Dispose of these threats in Za'Tual, $r, and watch the might of the trolls weaken.
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay 3 Zandalari Spiritbinders, 3 Zandalari Beastcallers, and 3 Zandalari Jaguar Warriors.
